00084 sub pretty_print_rh { 
00085     shift if UNIVERSAL::isa($_[0] => __PACKAGE__);
00086     my $rh = shift;
00087     my $indent = shift || 0;
00088     my $out = "";
00089     my $type = ref($rh);
00090 
00091     if (defined($type) and $type) {
00092         $out .= " type = $type; ";
00093     } elsif (! defined($rh )) {
00094         $out .= " type = UNDEFINED; ";
00095     }
00096     return $out." " unless defined($rh);
00097     
00098     if ( ref($rh) =~/HASH/ or "$rh" =~/HASH/ ) {
00099         $out .= "{\n";
00100         $indent++;
00101         foreach my $key (sort keys %{$rh})  {
00102             $out .= "  "x$indent."$key => " . pretty_print_rh( $rh->{$key}, $indent ) . "\n";
00103         }
00104         $indent--;
00105         $out .= "\n"."  "x$indent."}\n";
00106 
00107     } elsif (ref($rh)  =~  /ARRAY/ or "$rh" =~/ARRAY/) {
00108         $out .= " ( ";
00109         foreach my $elem ( @{$rh} )  {
00110             $out .= pretty_print_rh($elem, $indent);
00111         
00112         }
00113         $out .=  " ) \n";
00114     } elsif ( ref($rh) =~ /SCALAR/ ) {
00115         $out .= "scalar reference ". ${$rh};
00116     } elsif ( ref($rh) =~/Base64/ ) {
00117         $out .= "base64 reference " .$$rh;
00118     } else {
00119         $out .=  $rh;
00120     }
00121     
00122     return $out." ";
